						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Pedestal of a hero-stone standing near the Iśvara temple at Rāmatīrtha about two miles from the village.</hi></p>						

						<p>A.D. 973.</p>						

						<p>This incomplete record is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 895, Śrīmukha, Vaiśākha, Puṇṇame, Monday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 973, April 20,</hi> the weekday being, however, Sunday.</p>						

						<p>The inscription seems to record the death of Nāḻchuga, younger brother of Kāḷamma.</p>						

						</summary>
